title: What will Apple announce on Wednesday? - Channel3000
text:
Luckily, there are enough rumors and hints flying around online to give us a pretty good idea of what to expect at next week's big Apple press event. Apple will almost definitely upgrade its iPhones, likely introduce a new Apple TV, and maybe launch a large iPad Pro.
